Class Summary
NewURLyBirdHotelDialog This abstract class extends the JDialog class It draws to the user interface required components thats Dialog needs to create a new URLyBirdHotel record which will be added to the Database
URLyBirdAloneFrame This class extends URLyBirdApplicationFrame to display the Alone Frame User Interface for the user to interact with when running in a non networking environment mode
URLyBirdApplicationFrame This is an abstract class that constructs the layout/design of the Application user interface.
URLyBirdClientFrame This class extends URLyBirdApplicationFrame to display the client Frame User Interface for the user to interact with
URLyBirdConfigDialog This Class handles the URLyBird Configuration dialog User Interface, manages the components the dialog will contain in respect to the mode the application is running on to fit the Requirement.
URLyBirdServerFrame This Object extends the JFrame class to display the Server Graphical User Interface necessary for the user to start and communicate with the Server and its necessary components and resources
URLyBirdTableModel This class extends the AbstractTableModel class of the java library which populates the table to present the data
